at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.connection

Class SensorDataListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.ac.tuwien.ict.andropicar.rmcs.connection.SensorDataListener

  • public class SensorDataListener
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is being used by the RMCSs interfaces to know what DistanceSensorData should be forwarded to what ISensorDataListener.
    It is essentially a Tuple, with one attribute being the ISensorDataListener that wants to receive updates about sensor-events and the other being a list of EDataTypes that should be forwarded to the listener.
    Equality between two instances of this class, is determined by listener.
    Author:
    Boeck
